<description>&lt;div class=&#34;alert alert-info small bg-info&#34; role=&#34;alert&#34;&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;text-muted&#34;&gt;code for article&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/pfeilbr/node-odata-playground&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;fab fa-github fa-sm&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&amp;nbsp;pfeilbr/node-odata-playground&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;node-odata-playground&#34;&gt;node-odata-playground&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an example of a custom OData 4.0 provider that can be consumed by
salesforce &lt;a href=&#34;https://developer.salesforce.com/trailhead/en/lightning_connect/lightning_connect_introduction&#34;&gt;Lightning Connect&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
